;; asobi 遊び — seed play/expression graph (real, PUBLIC cultural commons + enclosures)
;; ADR-2606073200 · vocabulary: asobi-ontology (00-contracts/schemas/asobi-ontology.kotoba.edn)
;;
;; SCOPE GUARD (constitutional, G1 — read first):
;;   - asobi is a PARTICIPATION / ACCESS map of the freed-time telos, NEVER an engagement /
;;     attention / popularity ranking. NO retention metric, NO recommend-for-time, NO
;;     per-work popularity score. Addictive/spectacle design is unrepresentable (§1.13).
;;   - The lens is PARTICIPATION-openness (who can take part) vs ENCLOSURE (paywall /
;;     attention-platform / lock), routed to OPENING. karma lives ONLY on edges
;;     (:en/access-load; N1).
;;
;; SOURCING: license / public-record facts (public-domain status, open licenses, free public
;;   institutions) are :authoritative; the SAMPLE is a bounded illustrative seed
;;   (:representative coverage), NOT exhaustive. No fabricated coverage. Access categories
;;   are DISCLOSED facts, never asobi adjudications (N3).

